text:
The Signature Wanton Noodle has generous amount of char siew, fried meat dumplings, boiled meat dumplings and greens on curly thin egg noodle. It is a delicious dish.

Wonder why someone go around and give all the stalls in Bukit Batok West Hawker Centre ratings of 3 just to write a short description without trying the dishes. It is so unfair to the F&B operators here. Google Maps is full of rubbishes from people so eager to be "Top Reviewer" and not giving proper reviews.

A new hawker stall at the new Bukit Batok West Hawker Center selling wanton noodle.

The stall name is just a generic old signature wonton noodles.
